Third-party deduction hooks
Use the available hooks in the interfaces
curam.core.impl.PreCreateThirdPartyDeductionILIs and
curam.core.impl.PostCreateThirdPartyDeductionILIs to perform custom business
processing before and after the creation of third-party deduction instruction line items. For more
information, see the Javadoc for the associated class.
